==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Nonelectric
<hw>Non`e*lec"tric</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>A
substance that is not an insulator (i. e., an electric); that which
transmits electricity, as a metal; a conductor.</def>
<mark>[archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
